data.description: Welcome to this move in ready 3 bedroom, 2 bathroom, 1 car garage home located in Lakeland. This charming home is ready for it's new owner and features a formal dining room, kitchen with dining a breakfast nook, and a split bedroom floor plan. There is tile throughout the house, except for the master bedroom which has beautiful wood floors. Master bedroom has a walk in closet and it’s own private bathroom. There is a spacious backyard and the front porch would be the perfect spot for relaxing! The home is located close to everything Lakeland has to offer including shops, restaurants and the interstate. Schedule your showing today!
